<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span style="color:#006d98">فَالأَوَّلُ:</span> ثُبُوتُ الحُكْمَيْنِ بِالنَّصِّ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَالثَّانِي:</span> ثُبُوتُهُمَا نَقْلًا.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَالثَّالِثُ:</span> ثُبُوتُهُمَا بِخِطَابِ الشَّرْعِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَالرَّابِعُ:</span> أَنْ يَكُونَا عَمَلِيَّيْنِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَالخَامِسُ:</span> أَنْ يَكُونَا جُزْئِيَّيْنِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَالسَّادِسُ:</span> ثُبُوتُ التَّعَارُضِ بَيْنَهُمَا فِي المَعْنَى.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَالسَّابِعُ:</span> تَأَخَرُّ النَّاسِخِ عَنِ المَنْسُوخِ فِي زَمَنِ التَّشْرِيعِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَالنَّسْخُ أَرْبَعَةُ أَقْسَامٍ:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>١ - نَسْخُ قُرْآنٍ بِقُرْآنٍ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٢ - وَنَسْخُ سُنَّةٍ بِسُنَّةٍ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>٣ - وَنَسْخُ قُرْآنٍ بِسُنَّةٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>٤ - وَنَسْخُ سُنَّةٍ بِقُرْآنٍ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَطَرِيقَةُ مَعْرِفَةِ النَّسْخِ بِـ:</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>١ - لَفْظِ النَّصِّ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>٢ - أَوْ قَرِينَةٍ فِي النَّصِّ تَدُلُّ عَلَيْهِ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>٣ - أَوْ تَارِيخِ المُتَقَدِّمِ وَالمُتَأَخِّرِ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَأَنْوَاعُ النَّسْخِ ثَلَاثَةٌ:</span><a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>١ - نَسْخُ حُكْمٍ مَعَ بَقَاءِ التِّلَاوَةِ.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>٢ - وَنَسْخُ تِلَاوَةٍ مَعَ بَقَاءِ الحُكْمِ.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>٣ - وَنَسْخُ التِّلَاوَةِ وَالحُكْمِ.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>وقَدْ يَقَعُ نَسْخُ الحُكْمِ مَرَّتَيْنِ.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وَشَرَائِعُ مَنْ قَبْلَنَا:</span> شَرْعٌ لَنَا، غَيْرُ مَنْسُوخَةٍ، إِلَّا مَا قَامَ فِي شَرْعِنَا عَلَى خِلَافِهِ.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>تَفْسِيرُ القُرْآنِ<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>وَالتَّفْسيِرُ - اصْطِلَاحًا -: عِلْمٌ يُفْهَمُ بِهِ القُرْآنُ.<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>